msgstr "|system| 使用此选项卡可以定义矢量图层的常规设置。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:114
msgid "Source tab in vector Layer Properties dialog"
msgstr "矢量图层属性对话框中的源选项卡"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:117
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "设置"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:119
msgid ""
"Set a :guilabel:`Layer name` different from the layer filename that will be "
"used to identify the layer in the project (in the :guilabel:`Layers Panel`, "
"with expressions, in print layout legend, ...)"
msgstr ""
"设置 :guilabel:`图层名` 与用于识别工程中的图层文件名不同 (在 :guilabel:`图层面板` 中，使用表达式，在打印布局图例中，等等)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:122
msgid ""
"Depending on the data format, select the :guilabel:`Data source encoding` if"
" not correctly detected by QGIS."
msgstr "具体取决于数据格式，如果QGIS未正确检测到，请选择 :guilabel:`数据源编码` 。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:128
msgid ""
"Displays the layer's :ref:`Assigned Coordinate Reference System (CRS) "
"<layer_crs>`. You can change the layer's CRS, selecting a recently used one "
"in the drop-down list or clicking on |setProjection| :sup:`Select CRS` "
"button (see :ref:`crs_selector`). Use this process only if the CRS applied "
"to the layer is a wrong one or if none was applied. If you wish to reproject"
" your data into another CRS, rather use layer reprojection algorithms from "
"Processing or :ref:`Save it into another layer <general_saveas>`."
msgstr ""
"显示图层的 :ref:`指定坐标参照系 (CRS) <layer_crs>` 。您可以更改图层的CRS，在下拉列表中选择最近使用的CRS，或单击 "
"|setProjection| :sup:`选择CRS` 按钮 (请参阅 :ref:`crs_selector` "
")。仅当应用于图层的CRS错误或未应用任何CRS时，才使用此方法。如果您希望将数据重投影到另一个CRS，请使用图层重投影算法进行处理或 "
":ref:`将其另存为其他图层 <general_saveas>` 。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:4197
msgid "setProjection"
msgstr "setProjection"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:151
msgid ":guilabel:`Update extents` information for a layer."
msgstr "为图层 :guilabel:`更新范围` 信息。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:157
#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:204
msgid "Query Builder"
msgstr "查询构建器"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:163
msgid ""
"The Query Builder provides an interface that allows you to define a subset "
"of the features in the layer using a SQL-like WHERE clause and to display "
"the result in the main window. As long as the query is active, only the "
"features corresponding to its result are available in the project."
msgstr ""
"查询构建器提供了一个界面，允许您使用类似SQL的WHERE子句定义图层中要素的子集，并在主窗口中显示结果。只要查询处于激活状态，工程中就只有与其结果相对应的要素可用。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:169
msgid ""
"You can use one or more layer attributes to define the filter in the ``Query"
" Builder``. The use of more than one attribute is shown in "
":numref:`Figure_vector_querybuilder`. In the example, the filter combines "
"the attributes"
msgstr ""
"可以使用一个或多个图层属性在 ``查询构建器`` 中定义过滤条件。多个属性的使用如 "
":numref:`Figure_vector_querybuilder` 所示。在该示例中，过滤器组合了多个属性。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:174
msgid ""
"``toa`` (``DateTime`` field: ``cast(\"toa\" as character) > '2017-05-17'`` "
"and ``cast(\"toa\" as character) < '2019-12-24T18:00:00'``),"
msgstr ""
"``toa`` (``DateTime`` 字段: ``cast(\"toa\" as character) > '2017-05-17'`` 和 "
"``cast(\"toa\" as character) < '2019-12-24T18:00:00'``),"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:176
msgid "``name`` (``String`` field: ``\"name\" > 'S'``) and"
msgstr "``name`` (``String`` field: ``\"name\" > 'S'``) 和"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:177
msgid "``FID`` (``Integer`` field: ``FID > 10``)"
msgstr "``FID`` (``Integer`` field: ``FID > 10``)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:179
msgid ""
"using the AND, OR and NOT operators and parenthesis. This syntax (including "
"the DateTime format for the ``toa`` field) works for GeoPackage datasets."
msgstr "使用AND、OR和NOT运算符和括号。此语法 (包括 ``toa`` 字段的日期时间格式) 适用于GeoPackage数据集。"

